Bio: Recently confirmed by the elders of the internet as being "the best band in the world going by the name of deathdefyingspying" - these boys have some huge expectations to live up to. After accepting such a massive accolade, singer Paul was quoted as saying " I'm made up, but its not about the awards, the glory, the beautiful girls, the yachts and rolling around in my own filth and money - its all about producing something together, and something for the fans - they're the real people, they're who we do it for. This is for them"
